% Agda Tutorial


Usage
-----

An online HTML version can be found at

https://people.inf.elte.hu/divip/AgdaTutorial/Index.html


Local Builds
------------

The HTML files were generated by `agdapandoc` which is
a slightly modified version of the Agda compiler.

`agdapandoc` can be installed by installing the darcs version of
Agda and intalling the `PandocAgda` package from HackageDB
(whith `cabal install PandocAgda`).

See the Makefile how to use `agdapandoc`.


Development
-----------

This Agda tutorial is under development.

Any contribution is welcome, please send patches to
divipp@gmail.com
Please send small patches first.


